U.K.’s Baird to Be Named U.K. Trade & Investment Chief, Sky Says

-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 
2011-05-09T19:09:07Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-09/u-k-s-baird-to-be-named-u-k-trade-investment-chief-sky-says.html
U.K. Trade & Investment will tomorrow
announce the appointment of Nick Baird as the organization’s new
chief executive officer, replacing Andrew Cahn, who stepped down
in January, Sky News reported, citing people familiar with the
matter.  Baird, director-general for  Europe  and globalization at the
Foreign Office, will take up the post at the government’s trade
agency later this year, Sky said.  A UKTI spokeswoman declined to comment when contacted by
Bloomberg News while saying an announcement will be made
tomorrow.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Blanche Gatt in London at 
 bgatt@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge at 
 ckeatinge@bloomberg.net . 